As leaders in landscape creation with over 20 years of horticulture and design experience, we can make your landscaping dreams come true. No job is too large or small and each one is engineered to add curb appeal and value to your home. The enthusiasm for every project, the synthesis of ideas and the commitment to superlative quality inspire the creative expressions found in our wonderfully crafted outdoor environments.

Landscape Designer

SIGNATURE DESIGNS

Wayne and Kathy H.I.

We were fortunate to find these two delightful gentlemen. They truly love their job –they will put a lot of love into your garden.

Bob Bishopric

We are very much enjoying Paul and Tom’s expertise and company as they completely re-habilitate and beautify our 1/2 acre on Merritt Island.

Barbara Knick

Tom Jones and Paul Watson are two of my favorite people. You can’t go wrong working with them!

Tom Campbell

This landscape and design company is the best!!! They have done a lot of work for me and I could not give them a higher recommendation. The best part is that they give great customer service and provide high quality work. You cannot go wrong with them.

Kasie Hope Brautigam

We were very pleased with the landscaping done by Paul and Tom. They were honest, hard working ,trustworthy people. They did extensive work on our irrigation system, getting it to the new beds they created.

Vicki Tull

Tom and Paul and the entire team at The Master’s Touch have transformed our yard and garden. After 2 projects we are thrilled with the results – they took a bland, boring area and turned it into a back yard oasis that we truly enjoy every day.

Joy Goldstein

Both Tom and Paul helped us transform our planting beds. Many people have walked by and said to me how great everything looks.

Larry Sills

We went with a different landscaper last year for our backyard. When we were ready to complete the landscaping with our front and side yards, we decided to try The Master’s Touch. Wow, what a difference!

Chuck Fontana

Paul and Tom are highly skilled and professional landscapers. A plan was devised to refresh the-areas around the house keeping some trees/flowers/grass etc and adding new items.
